Coon_Rapids.Andover High School (Minnesota):
Andover High School is a four-year public high school located at 2115 Andover Blvd, Andover, Minnesota.
Andover High School is a part of the Anoka-Hennepin School District 11 and is one of five traditional high schools in the school district. This high school first opened in 2002 and is the newest high school in District 11.
